# Raw dashboard exports dropped into onboarding/ for /onboard-dashboard to
# read — never commit these. Only the generated registry YAML and the
# generated *_validation_summary.md belong in git; the export itself can
# contain internal contacts/access instructions and is superseded by those
# two generated files.
